  "commit_message": "feat(deactivate): trace wrap + unset helpers (DEV-86)\n\nWrap deactivate output in trace mode when the tracelevel (threaded from _FLOX_SUBSYSTEM_VERBOSITY) is >= 2, and unset the _activate_d / _flox_activate_tracer helper exports at the end of deactivate. zsh additionally clears _flox_activate_tracelevel and keeps its trace wrap in activate.d/zsh rather than in the generator.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
